Task 1: LED Alert for Object Detection
Goal:
Turn ON an LED when an object is closer than 10 cm.

Additional Wiring:
LED to Arduino Pin D7

Task 2: Display Distance on LCD (I2C 16x2 Display)
Wiring:
LCD I2C Pin	Arduino Pin
VCC	5V
GND	
SDA	A4 (Uno) / 20 (Mega)
SCL	A5 (Uno) / 21 (Mega)

Task 3: Wireless Distance Monitoring via Bluetooth (HC-05/HC-06)
Wiring: 
TXD	D2 (Software Serial RX)
RXD	D3 (Software Serial TX)

